<h3>&nbsp;</h3>
<div class="s-rich-text-wrapper" style="display: block;">
<p class="s-rich-text-wrapper">Brawlers</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="s-item-text">
<div class="s-component s-text">
<div>
<div class="s-component-content s-font-body" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">
<div class="s-rich-text-wrapper" style="display: block;">
<p class="s-rich-text-wrapper">The best brawlers to unlock with gems in Brawl Stars include:</p>
<p><span style="display: inline-block;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>-Spike: Spike is a legendary brawler with an attack that is great for targeting enemies in Gem Grab maps with open spaces. His versatility and ability to slow down enemies carrying gems make him a valuable choice for Gem Grab.</p>
<p><span style="display: inline-block;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>-Gene: Gene is a mythic brawler whose "Magic Hand" super attack can be a game-changer in Gem Grab matches. His ability to drag enemies towards him, smashing through walls and obstacles, is essential for bringing the enemy carrying gems closer to your team.</p>
<p><span style="display: inline-block;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>-Shelly: Shelly, the first brawler players use in the game, is lethal at close range. Her ability to instantly teleport back to her turret and take all the gems she has collected with her can be a strategic advantage in Gem Grab matches.</p>
<p><span style="display: inline-block;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>-Tara: Tara, a mythic brawler, is versatile and helps reveal the opposition's location. Her basic attack and gadgets are effective at close range, making her a valuable asset in Gem Grab matches where knowing the enemy's location and gem count is crucial.</p>
<p><span style="display: inline-block;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>-Nita: Nita, the second brawler on the trophy road, is another excellent choice for <strong>Gem Grab</strong>. With moderate health and attack range, she can position herself in the center of the action while collecting gems. Her "Furry Friend" can act as a great distraction, aiding in gem collection and team strategy.</p>
<p><span style="display: inline-block;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>By unlocking and utilizing these brawlers in Gem Grab matches, players can enhance their gameplay experience and increase their chances of success in collecting and protecting gems effectively.</p>
